* Results by Gender: Displays race results filtered by gender.
*   When to use:    After the race to review results by gender.
*   How to use:     Double-click to display the results in the Browse window.

ResultsByGender.rsm M Finish
ResultsByGender.rsm F Finish

* Examples for other events:
* ResultsByGender.rsm M Time
* ResultsByGender.rsm F Time